{"type": "article", "id": 6192, "title": "耐克紧跟阿迪达斯上线了一个APP，专售运动鞋", "description": "通过 APP 买球鞋变得越来越容易了。", "date": "2015-02-13T12:57:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1036, "name": "耐克"}, {"id": 1297, "name": "阿迪达斯"}, {"id": 29, "name": "Top 15"}], "category": 18, "column": null, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 62, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607134204kIfmKWaVnDdg7Tzv.png", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t距阿迪达斯发布 APP 不到一周，耐克也发布了一款卖鞋的 App ：<a href=\"http://news.nike.com/news/nike-introduces-nike-snkrs-app-for-the-love-of-kicks\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color:#FFFFFF;\">SNKRS</a>。通过这款 APP ，顾客不仅可以买到耐克官方发布的鞋款，还可以在“状态提醒”里实时查看订单状态。顾客可以将自己的鞋码信息、颜色偏好存储在 APP 中以节省购鞋时间，在每一款球鞋背后，APP 还会呈现其设计故事。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134201Z5cyORWkXQqvnt08.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.46875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134201dgSF93a7CUqVWvEG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.46875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060713420252VnA7T6kUO94pIZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.46875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t图片来自耐克官方网站\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t这些功能听起来很熟悉？没错，因为在<a href=\"http://fashionista.com/2015/02/kanye-west-adidas-yeezy-fashion-week\" target=\"_blank\"> </a><span style=\"white-space:normal;\"><a href=\"http://fashionista.com/2015/02/kanye-west-adidas-yeezy-fashion-week\" target=\"_blank\">Kanye West 新款上架</a>的前一周</span>，阿迪达斯已率先发布了这样一款 APP ，APP 叫作<a href=\"http://sneakernews.com/2015/02/03/use-this-app-to-reserve-upcoming-kanye-west-x-adidas-sneaker/\" target=\"_blank\"> Confirmed</a> ，顾客预定的运动鞋一旦到店，APP 便会发出震动，提醒购买者去最近的实体店取货，这项业务只在纽约地区推行。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071342024Xb2duFUs9l8yIMi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6703125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134202oP0AkUmxrn9zK6SJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6703125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134203ZIVLTecaWk0h4mso.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6703125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t耐克推出的 APP 目前还处在试下载和体验阶段，2 月 12 日到 15 日，如果你恰好在纽约，可以去 Zoom City SNKRS Station 试用一下。正式版本将于今年春季登陆 APP\r\nStore 。我们很好奇，未来哪款 APP 的装机量和活跃度会更高？\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607134203gsjLE61k43rMOGot.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n题图来自：<a href=\"http://news.nike.com/news/nike-introduces-nike-snkrs-app-for-the-love-of-kicks\" target=\"_blank\">耐克官网</a>\n\n\n"}